<cl=F0F010>Guide:<cl=00FF00> Ha! The old warrior won't leave his post! Well, your sword should put him at rest.<br><br>

<cl=FFFFFF>Take the sword by clicking it.<br>
Click the left mouse button to make a strike.<br>
The target should be close enough to be damaged by your blows.<br><br>
